    Fit a model for mean and variance

    fit_meanvar.Rd

    Fit a model for mean and variance

    Usage

    fit_meanvar(x, tau, ...)

    Arguments

    x

    A time series

    tau

    a set of indices representing a changepoint set

    ...

    arguments passed to stats::lm()

    See also

    Other model-fitting: fit_lmshift(), fit_meanshift(), fit_nhpp_region(), new_fun_cpt()

    Examples

    fit_meanvar(CET, tau = c(42, 330))
